WEBVTT

00:10:27.449 --> 00:10:30.402
But there is the good news,

00:10:30.426 --> 00:10:31.576
good signs.

00:10:32.220 --> 00:10:35.580
Coalitions of stakeholders

00:10:35.604 --> 00:10:40.481
are now coming together
to try to transform the food system

00:10:40.505 --> 00:10:42.890
with one shared goal:

00:10:42.914 --> 00:10:47.466
how to produce enough
healthy food for everyone,

00:10:47.490 --> 00:10:48.986
at the same time,

00:10:49.010 --> 00:10:52.130
to try to cut, to sharply reduce,

00:10:52.154 --> 00:10:56.395
the footprint from the food system
on the global commons.

00:10:58.983 --> 00:11:00.682
I had an opportunity